import React from 'react'
import { Header, Image, Table ,Button} from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Tablee = (props) => 


(
  

    
  <>
 

    <Table.Body>
      <Table.Row>
        <Table.Cell>
          <Header as='h4' image>
            <Header.Content>
              {props.boke.name}
              
            </Header.Content>
          </Header>
        </Table.Cell>
<Table.Cell>{props.boke.bookingـdate.split("T")[0]}</Table.Cell>
<Table.Cell>{props.boke.status}</Table.Cell>
{props.userType && <Table.Cell> 
    <Button  inverted color='red' onClick={()=>props.status(props.boke._id , "Rejection")}>
    Rejection 
      </Button>
      <Button onClick={()=>props.status(props.boke._id , "Accept")} inverted color='green'>
      Accept
      </Button>
</Table.Cell> }
      </Table.Row>
    </Table.Body>
 </>
)
export default Tablee
